'limit redraws to 30fps
'(reduce CPU usage)
_LIMIT 30

'for speed, default to long (32-bit) for variables
'(and function returns, if not otherwise specified)
DEFLNG a-z

'generic 'index' counters
DIM i, j, k, h, w, x, y AS _UNSIGNED LONG

